My misexplanation.   I was planning to move the library out of the
way, rename deflibs and rebuild it.   Then when I recompile I get ????
errors for tokens from the "Missing" library.   These I can replace
with NCS commands or I can examine the offending include file using
the "Old" deflibs if I can't work out what the token should have been.
As far as I can tell, this is the only way to Guarantee to replace all
commands in one library.

