> frames (yeah right) so for a "lame" format it does quite well....
> 
> To boost the frame rate you could always go for 320x150 for that cinematic
> feel......
> 
> Blitzwing

Don`t forget that if CDXL animation was 320*128 pixels there exists 
some screenmodes which half the number of vertical lines.  
Basically the 128 pixels would be full screen and with no slowdown.

Steven





