Content-Disposition: attachment; filename="Getnameoftask.asc"
Content-Description: Very small bit of code :) very useful

WBStartup
*task.Process=FindTask_(0)
NPrint Peek$(*task\pr_Task\tc_Node\ln_Name)
ClickMouse
End

