@NODE "Mail_250" "Re: Double precision float"
 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Wed, 17 Feb 1999 12:58:25 +0000
 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Wed, 17 Feb 1999 12:57:32 +0000
