@NODE "Mail_269" "Re: End of mildred!!!"
 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Thu, 18 Feb 1999 12:43:38 +0000
 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Thu, 18 Feb 1999 12:41:15 +0000
