  o   +  \___  /   |____(____  /__|_|  /\___  > + |
  |   |      \/              \/      \/     \/  | |_
  __  +     ________                 __         + __
 /__  |     \______ \  __ __   ____ |  | __     | |_
 \_|  +      |    |  \|  |  \_/ ___\|  |/ /     + |_
