Hi,

I really, really need some help with arexx. All i want to do is send a command
to a port, and get a return string and/or error code.

It's really important, my proggy is useless without the arexx. It was working
fine until i noticed my memory slowly draining away when i run my proggy, so
i managed to trace it down to the RI Arexx lib's arexx commands not freeing
