@NODE "Mail_516" "Mildred extensions"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Sat, 20 Feb 1999 22:15:15 +0000
 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Sat, 20 Feb 1999 22:14:07 +0000
From: "Paul" <paulwest@stationone.demon.co.uk>
Organization: private
Date: 20 Feb 99 22:12:22 +0000
Subject: Mildred extensions

