@NODE "Mail_540" "Re: Mildred reservations + Screen.RastPort vs Bitmap"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Fri, 26 Feb 1999 15:01:49 +0000
 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Fri, 26 Feb 1999 14:57:20 +0000
