> i can't figure it out! my program should change directory
> after exit.... so i put in my code

> [...]

> i dosen't work! shell prompt shows this same path that i start
> this program, so i remove this "nil" stuff but it STILL dose't
> work....

My guess is that the cd command you're executing is simply changing the
directory for the process that starts when you do the execute command, but
not the process that is running your program.  To do what you want, maybe
you could run the program in a script that changes the directory after
executing your program?


