First of all, you have to make sure you detach the GTList (DetachGTlist I=
 think) then you should be able to free it, allthough why you would want =
to is beond me.

> Dim SCRtags.TagItem(11)
>  SCRtags(0)\ti_Tag=3D#SA_DisplayID,SDisplay
>  SCRtags(1)\ti_Tag=3D#SA_Overscan,SOscan
>  SCRtags(2)\ti_Tag=3D#SA_Depth,SDpth
>  SCRtags(3)\ti_Tag=3D#SA_Width,SWidh
