    FileInput 0
    p$=3DEdit$(255)             ; reads up to 255 characters wide (or to =
first newline)
    PopInput                  ; or whatever you need to redirect input
    CloseFile 0
EndIf

Also, there's a little library called config.library which I got going,
but to be honest, this way is just as good...

See ya,
