Hi Paul,
        If you've managed to make it back from the hills :) you will be able
to read this.

The NetDOCK-2 images are COMPLETELY customisable. Right down to the palette.
Obviously it's best suited to your workbench palette, but if you use NI or
whatever, just design new icons for it!

All this is of course assuming that I can figure out how to wrap the window
round to another row of icons if the set figure won't fit on one (99 icons
on one row, can it be done?)

If u want to send in some images to me, then feel free!

