el, you get some error message back from printer.device. Simply sending e=
verything to PRT: is sorta only one way communication, I mean how is prin=
te.device going to know whee to send error messages ? Anyway, I don't kno=
w if this makes any sense at all, it just seems obvious. (So it's probabl=
y wrong, that's the way it is with intuition, the obvious way is allways =
wrong :o>)


