Long story short, fdconvert botches up the opening of resources and
devices.  I've fixed it in my version (does the person who wrote that
newfdconvert want to integrate my changes?), and I've included an
archive of fixed amigalibs resources and devices.  I don't know what lib
numbers are used (the same ones as the originals I think), so be careful

--
Julian Kinraid
