@NODE "Mail_819" "Re: Setting the stack size"
From: Mikkel =?iso-8859-1?Q?L=F8kke?= <FlameDuck@usa.net>
Date: Thu, 11 Feb 1999 16:26:17 +0200
Organization: A97
Subject: Re: Setting the stack size
