@ENDNODE
@NODE "Mail_857" "Re: sizeofbitmaps"
From: Curt Esser <camge@ix.netcom.com>
Date: Sat, 06 Feb 1999 16:46:43 -0500
Subject: Re: sizeofbitmaps

Hi david

On 06-Feb-99, david white wrote:
> Hi,
> 
>    Simple question this time (I should already know this!)
> 
>        How d'ya calculate the memory required by a bitmap that is (x)
> width (y) height and (d) depth?
> 
> CYa!
Later...

bytes=x*y*d/8

for a shape, add 1 to the depth to account for the cookie.


