There is one other way too as you can see from the example code you wrote=

the current variable is handled in D0 (if not newtype flaot string etc)
so just put
x.l=3Dx.l
move.l d0,<usefull-address-or-reg>

And I think this can be optimized in the same way as the get/putreg thing=
s
but is faster while testing and building the thing up.

