@NODE "Mail_987" "VisualGUI needs BETA TESTERS - Come and get it!"
From: "Jobbdirekte" <alphade@c2i.net>
Subject: VisualGUI needs BETA TESTERS - Come and get it!
Date: Wed, 17 Feb 1999 08:27:52 +0100
	boundary="----=_NextPart_000_0014_01BE5A4F.696203E0"

This is a multi-part message in MIME format.

------=_NextPart_000_0014_01BE5A4F.696203E0
	charset="iso-8859-1"
Encoding: quoted-printable

What is VisualGui??

Basicly, its a new user-interface and application model written in =
Blitz2.
I am posting it here to get help tacking down bugs, perhaps replacing =
some of the routines with
assembler, and generaly making the system better.
It is a smi-real GUI system, using it's own layers etc...

Please get back to me with informasjon.
Some docs and full sourcecode in  the archive



